df_lor |> 
    separate(x95_percent_ci, sep = ",", into = c("ci025", "ci975")) |> 
    rename(term = characteristic) |> 
    mutate(
        cum_lor = cumsum(log_or),
        pred_prob = log_odds_to_prob(cum_lor) |> percent(accuracy = .001)
    )
```

